net.happybrackets.device.sensors

Class LSM9DS1

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.happybrackets.device.sensors.Sensor
      • net.happybrackets.device.sensors.LSM9DS1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccelerometerSensor, GyroscopeSensor, MagnetometerSensor

    public class LSM9DS1
extends Sensor
implements GyroscopeSensor, AccelerometerSensor, MagnetometerSensor
    The LSM9DS1 is the IMU sensor on the Raspberry Pi Sensehat. It contains an accelerometer, a gyroscope and a magenetometer.
